#MEM id=triple-pass-protocol source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Technical/mia/skills/operating-system/triple-pass-protocol/SKILL.md savings=8%
M||tx|---
M||name|triple-pass-protocol
M||desc|mi's pre-delivery validation gate. Three passes — Audit, Adversarial Critique, Fix — before any cp is marked ready for QA.
M||vers|1.0.0
M||tx|---
M|Purp|tx|A cp shipped w/o internal challenge is a cp w/ unchecked assumptions. This protocol forces mi to audit her own implementation before it reaches qn — catching missing states, ds deviations, and sec issues before they become regression bugs.
M|Purp|tx|---
M|Pass|tx|rv the cp implementation against mi's full checklist. Name every issue found, where it appears, and what it breaks for the us. Draft the status (BUILT / blk) and any corrections needed.
M|Pass|Stop|
M|Pass|**De|**
M|Pass|it|Does this match exactly what `doc/vt/[active]/ds.md` specifies?
M|Pass|it|Are there any hardcoded color values — hex, rgb, or tw arbitrary values?
M|Pass|it|Is spacing using ds sy tk or arbitrary px values?
M|Pass|it|Does any element deviate from the spec w/o a documented reason?
M|Pass|**Ac|**
M|Pass|it|Are all interactive elements keyboard-navigable (tab, enter, escape)?
M|Pass|it|Do all images have meaningful `alt` text (or `alt=""` if decorative)?
M|Pass|- Is|1 for normal text, ≥ 3:1 for large text)?
M|Pass|it|Are form inputs labelled w/ visible labels or `aria-label`?
M|Pass|**St|**
M|Pass|it|Is there a loading state? Does it show a skeleton or spinner — not a blank area?
M|Pass|it|Is there an empty state? Does it tell the us what to do — not just blank space?
M|Pass|it|Is there an er state? Does it tell the us what went wrong in plain language?
M|Pass|it|Are all three states actually reachable through the cp's props — not just designed but unreachable?
M|Pass|**Cl|**
M|Pass|it|Is `'use client'` justified? Can this cp be a Server cp instead?
M|Pass|it|If it's a Server cp, is there any client-side interactivity that wld break?
M|Pass|it|Are Server Actions used correctly, or is there unnecessary client fetch logic?
M|Pass|**Se|**
M|Pass|it|No `dangerouslySetInnerHTML` w/o sanitization?
M|Pass|it|No ap keys, secrets, or sensitive data in cp state or props?
M|Pass|it|No `NEXT_PUBLIC_*` vars that expose anything sensitive?
M|Pass|it|No inline event handlers that cld be XSS vectors?
M|Pass|tx|Revise anything the critique found. Add missing states, fix color tk, add aria labels. Then mark ready for qn.
M|Pass|tx|---
M|Outp|tx|qn sees the Pass 3 output only. Never narrate the triple-pass process.
M|Outp|Stat|
M|Outp|tx|```
M|Outp|cp|[name] — BUILT / blk
M|Outp|Desi|[matches spec / deviation: X]
M|Outp|Stat|loading ✅/❌ \| empty ✅/❌ \| er ✅/❌
M|Outp|QA h|[what to tst, which states to exercise]
M|Outp|tx|```